|6 |          └─SORT                      |           |2       |75          |
|7 |            └─NESTED-LOOP JOIN        |           |2       |74          |
|8 |              ├─MERGE JOIN            |           |2       |45          |
|9 |              │ ├─TABLE FULL SCAN     |STORE      |12      |3           |
|10|              │ └─SORT                |           |2       |42          |
|11|              │   └─NESTED-LOOP JOIN  |           |2       |41          |
|12|              │     ├─TABLE FULL SCAN |ITEM       |2       |13          |
|13|              │     └─TABLE RANGE SCAN|STORE_SALES|2       |16          |
|14|              └─TABLE GET             |DATE_DIM   |1       |16          |
=============================================================================
